{"tid":2452180,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"leaps/poor man's covered call","createTime":"2021-03-18T16:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T18:35:56.000Z","uid":22046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"89e6e6065be36445ac91359c0e98227706b38f32","tid":2452180,"uid":22046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T16:06:26.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲做緊？<br />\nbasic野唔講 相信入得黎都有基本concept <br />\n亦唔想太多人講呢個topic<br />\n<br />\n依家做緊2/3倉 SPY 2yr deep itm leaps(delta0.7) + monthly covered call (delta 0.3)希望食埋theta decay<br />\n希望可以穩定地增長<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家諗緊rebalancing strategy/慢慢係youtube學緊python basic 野希望遲d可以做到back test<br />\n<br />\n不過都驚突然一個bear market坐兩年都回唔到本<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JjRsGa4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJjRsGa4.jpg&h=73e50112&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歷史上數據係有咁既風險<br />\n所以需要一個rebalancing/exit strategy<br />\n<br />\n一齊交流下, 善用不推文靜靜地贏<br />\n<br />\n警告：以上call option可以蝕到變零 新手請再三research先入場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k6MTBX7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk6MTBX7.png&h=f63c4cdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fvB8qRm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfvB8qRm.jpg&h=7b806214&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e0b5e869e5b17f7836302eeaaf492bba10c27c7","tid":2452180,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T16:30:51.000Z","msg":"backtest要有data<br />\n問題係option data好貴"},{"pid":"7d4a78ba1a3520fdc65c064eab8600b2c9c83279","tid":2452180,"uid":22046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e0b5e869e5b17f7836302eeaaf492bba10c27c7","tid":2452180,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T16:30:51.000Z","msg":"backtest要有data<br />\n問題係option data好貴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T16:46:09.000Z","msg":"leaps 應該可以靠估算 但cc有難度<br />\n唔緊要 我學住先都無壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" cl